reviewText:
Really only worth it for seeing some Fall footage of "The Joke" done live from 2002 and a few other songs. I wanted to like this a lot despte all the negative things I'd read. Worst of all was the bonus footage of "sentences" of a different MES chat that doesn't seem complete, like a dvd that is skipping while someone is talking.
Glad I supported the release anyway
it was OK, but not as good as it could've been.  the filmmakers seem to be a fan of one of the styles of music that the Fall do, and made a documentary about that
